{"tid":1464634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議停一停機場，等大家有精力做818遊行同埋機場公安嘅文宣","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:26:04.000Z","uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a46cd478f0111b9145a9e8cbc04e94d52b5dd84","tid":1464634,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"去機場雖然安全，但係要夠多人先有滿意嘅效果<br />\n<br />\n連續咁去機場會令到每日嘅人數逐步減少(好似呢排每個weekend兩三次遊行咁)<br />\n<br />\n去機場嘅文宣對象主要係國際，但係公安同埋818遊行呢兩單野嘅文宣主要係對香港人(特別係遊行)<br />\n<br />\n大家都需要時間儲物資、文宣同埋休息(始終唔係個個都可以無限精力咁出)<br />\n<br />\n我擔心嘅係因為機場令到818嘅遊行少左人，咁林鄭就可以大力帶風向。(大家都知道香港人好多勝利球迷，見個大遊行少左人，就容易轉軑)"},{"pid":"faa52af6be420734a2fe0eb893fc89007f4fb9da","tid":1464634,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:17:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8.18!!!  NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QBW03OD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQBW03OD.jpg&h=7dda7bb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DWjYQtD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDWjYQtD.png&h=93172175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKuaGAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKuaGAi.jpg&h=2c7d515e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9SyreVi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9SyreVi.jpg&h=02f1489c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5sL5vtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5sL5vtE.jpg&h=26c438eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31af4f18c4cd3a5b0cc77e710d162d34cff18bf3","tid":1464634,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-al